sub_title: Part owner, artist and designer at Studio Rozi / Owner and web designer at Mamo.hr
summary:
Motivated, socially committed, methodical and with a strong work ethic, these are, in short, the qualities that best define me professionally and which, to a certain extent, also show my personality.
‍
As I developed as an individual, gaining a strong awareness of all the social issues around me, it became clear that these elements would have to be incorporated into some of my designs. In this sense, throughout my academic career, and more recently, at a professional level, I always try to convey a strong personal touch in the projects I carry out.
‍
Therefore, my artistic development, above all, will always go through a continuous process of creative self-discovery and constant learning, experimenting with different techniques, tools and media in order to develop my projects more and more.
